description: A Chromium-based WPF/WinForms component that can be embedded into your .NET application to display modern web pages built with HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Silverlight etc.
releaseNotes:
DotNetBrowser 1.5.2 contains the following features and improvements:
			Cache storage has been implemented.
		    Environment validation has been disabled.
			The issue when Browser instances share proxy settings has been fixed.
			The issue when proxy authentication doesn't work has been fixed.
summary: Solution for integration of Chromium-based component into .NET applications.
title: DotNetBrowser
